## NOTE: The Emacs `rg` package always passes "--no-config", which means that it
## ignores the settings in this file.  Set Emacs variable
## `rg-command-line-flags`.

## I don't like this setting.
# # Don't let ripgrep vomit really long lines to my terminal.
# --max-columns=300

# Search hidden files by default.
--hidden

--smart-case

# Force ripgrep to sort its output by file name. (This disables parallelism, so it might be slower.)
--sort-files

# Follow symbolic links while recursively searching.
--follow

# Search inside compressed files (e.g., `.gz`).
--search-zip
